title: SIEGE IN THE NORTH - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Gameplay
description:
Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Gameplay - Today we have a massive siege battle in Medieval Kingdoms!  I command Sweden and my ally, Jackie Fish, commands Despotate of Epirus.  England has Invaded our land, and now we must fight!  The armies are on large, and I decide to sally out in this battle, it's quite interesting :D  Enjoy the Battle.

Jackie's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCNjxbL33FhDGeIOp3vd3ndg 

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
